results.title: Up and Around
results.description: Professor Xavier can walk for a day so Jubilee takes him roller-blading (of course); Hank and Warren re-build Harry's Hideaway.

results.title: For The Children!
results.description: The X-Men save a bus load of mutant kids from the Acolytes.

results.title: Nightlines
results.description: Xavier, Kelly, Graydon and Beast debate mutant rights on Night Line.

results.title: Legacies
results.description: The X-Men launch an all out assault on the Acolytes to retrieve Moira MacTaggert.

results.title: Epilog
results.description: Magneto isn't dead; Illyana has the legacy virus.

results.title: Dominion!
results.description: Forge is the Upstarts new target and Fitzroy gets there first.

results.title: Province
results.description: The X-Men save Forge from Fitzroy, and then have to save Fitzroy from Colossus.

results.title: Motions
results.description: The tragic death of Illyana to the Legacy Virus.

results.title: ...For What I Have Done
results.description: The X-Men gather for Illyana's funeral; Magneto brings Avalon to Earth and offers the X-Folk a chance to join his dream; Colossus says "Yes."

results.title: The Measure Of The Man
results.description: Iceman, Rogue and Bishop save Opal from a mysterious group of men in battle suits; Xavier asks Storm to steal for him.

results.title: Mortal Coils
results.description: Xavier battles Quicksilver in the Danger Room; Forge and Storm go on a date; Cameron Hodge kills Candy Southern all over again.

results.title: Bloodties Part Four: Night Fog
results.description: Genosha explodes into conflict as the X-Men and Avengers try to save Luna from Fabian Cortez.

results.title: Mixed Blessings
results.description: It's Thanksgiving Day and the X-Men celebrate by raking leaves and playing football; Scott and Jean are engaged (Wedding in X-Men #30).

results.title: ...When The Tigers Come At Night!
results.description: Story is a dream sequence where Xavier and Magneto talk about his past loves and the life he almost shared with Amelia Voght (the Acolyte).

results.title: Cable... Cyclops... Alone... Against The X-Cutioner!
...Show Me The Way To Go Home...
results.description: Cyclops is late for his own Bachelor Party as he and Cable save the White Queen from the X-Cutioner.

results.title: Putting The Cat Out
results.description: The power in X-Mansion goes down leaving Sabretooth to run wild with only Bishop and Jubilee standing in his way.

results.title: Storm... Yukio... At The Mercy Of Phalanx!
Romp
results.description: Storm, Gambit and Yukio take on the Phalanx; The mystery of the Iceman / White Queen switch deepens.

results.title: Hands Across The Water
results.description: The X-Men finish their battle with the Phalanx; The White Queen possesses Iceman's body.

results.title: Early Frost
results.description: The X-Men track the White Queen who has taken over Iceman's body; Emma learns that Fitzroy killed the Hellions.

results.title: Peers
results.description: There is trouble in Avalon as an Acolyte betrays Magneto.

results.title: The Phalanx Covenant - Generation Next Part One: Encounter
results.description: The Phalanx captures M; Banshee finds X-Mansion crawling with the Phalanx impersonating X-Men and he turns to Sabretooth for help.

results.title: The Phalanx Covenant - Generation Next Part Three: Enter Freely And Of Your Own Will
results.description: The next generation of mutants try to escape from the clutches of the Phalanx.

results.title: Moving Day
results.description: Xavier chooses Banshee and the White Queen to run Generation X; Jubilee leaves the X-Men for her new team.

results.title: Untapped Potential
results.description: Iceman takes Rogue home for dinner with the folks; Archangel and Psylocke decide to become a couple; Xavier learns in a dream that his son, Legion, is back and more powerful than ever.

results.title: The Son Rises In The East (Legion Quest Part One)
results.description: The X-Men try to stop a sane and dangerous Legion who now has the power to manipulate time; The team gets zapped back to the past when Legion travels there.

results.title: Auld Lang Syne [Legion Quest Part Three]
results.description: The X-Men continue their quest to keep Legion from killing Magneto in the past.

results.title: Generation Of Evil
results.description: The X-Folk play baseball; Callisto and Colossus come to the team to help gain control of a band of rogue Morlocks; During the battle, Storm rips out Marrow's heart.

results.title: Nature Of Evil
results.description: Xavier and Beast hold a press conference concerning the Legacy Virus; Gambit confronts Sabretooth with a number of his victims.

results.title: Whisper On The Wind
results.description: Joseph wakes up and tries to figure out who he is.

results.title: Precipice
results.description: Sabretooth stops pretending to be brain dead and escapes X-Mansion after gutting Psylocke.

results.title: Quest For The Crimson Dawn (Warriors Of The Ebon Night Conclusion)
results.description: The X-men make a deal with the Crimson Dawn to save Psylocke's life.

results.title: Iceman vs. Generation X's White Queen
The Splinter Of Our Discontent
results.description: Iceman confronts the White Queen about her invasions of his mind after she shared his body.

results.title: The Other Shoe...
results.description: Kelly warns Cyclops about Operation Zero Tolerance; Jean and Gambit break into the Pentagon and run across Bastion.
